entry.content: Canada Preparing For A Fascist America #usa #canada Canada says it’s creating a game plan for how to respond and deal with the United States if it takes a far-right authoritarian shift in next year’s Presidential election. They worry that the two Republican front runners will pull the US out of NATO and all of its other treaties including trade agreements, leaving Canada to fend for itself. They declined to comment on what the plan would look like but Europe and Canada have been strengthening ties since the Trump Presidency due to this explicit scenario. If push comes to shove, they could always build a wall.

entry.content: Russia Killed Leader Of Wagner #russia #ukraine Russia has killed the leader of Wagner. Russian state media says Prigo as well as at least 9 others passengers died when his jet crashed. Wagner is accusing Russia of shooting down the plane as he was leaving Moscow today. Initial flight data and video evidence seems to back that accusation. Wagner’s military commander is also reportedly among the dead. The CIA doesn’t call Putin the “ultimate Apostle of payback” for no reason.
